overview.en: Turbo USD Finance (USDT) is an independent USD-pegged stablecoin on BNB Smart Chain. The token is designed for fast, low-cost DeFi transactions with 1:1 USD backing and transparent reserves. NOT affiliated with Tether Holdings Limited.
overview.zh: Turbo USD Finance (USDT) 是 BNB 智能链上独立的美元锚定稳定币。该代币专为快速、低成本的 DeFi 交易而设计，具有 1:1 美元支持和透明的储备金。与 Tether Holdings Limited 无关联。
